p\u014d\u02bbaiapuni a\u02bbo: ʻO nā ʻanuʻu a CPU e hahai ai e hoʻokō i kahi ʻōlelo aʻo
hale ho\u02bbol\u0101l\u0101 superscalar: Hoʻolālā CPU hiki ke hoʻokō i nā ʻōlelo kuhikuhi he nui i kēlā me kēia pōʻai uaki
w\u0101nana l\u0101l\u0101: ʻenehana kahi e hoʻāʻo ai ka CPU e koho i ke ala e hele ai kahi kūlana
alahaka \u02bb\u0101kau: Chipset (nā ʻōnaehana kahiko) i hoʻopili i ka CPU me ka RAM a me nā kaʻa kaʻa wikiwiki
alahaka hema: Chipset (nā ʻōnaehana kahiko) i mālama i nā peripheral māmā a me I/O
hyperthreading: ʻO ka ʻenehana e ʻae ana i kahi core CPU hoʻokahi e ʻike ʻia ma ke ʻano he mau cores logical
risc: Hoʻoemi Instruction Set Computer - Hoʻolālā CPU me nā ʻōlelo maʻalahi
cisc: Kamepiula Aʻo Paʻakikī - Hoʻolālā CPU me nā ʻōlelo aʻoaʻo ikaika a paʻakikī
simd: Hoʻokahi Aʻo Nui ʻIkepili, ʻenehana no ka hoʻoili ʻana i ka ʻikepili i ka like
microarchitecture: ʻO nā kikoʻī hoʻokō kikoʻī o kahi hoʻonohonoho aʻoaʻo CPU
\u02bb\u014dnaehana ma kahi pu\u02bbupu\: Hoʻohui i nā ʻāpana he nui (CPU, GPU, a me nā mea ʻē aʻe) ma kahi pahu hoʻokahi
\u02bb\u014dnaehana ho\u02bbokomo: He ʻōnaehana kamepiula i hoʻolaʻa ʻia i kahi hana kikoʻī, pinepine i loko o kahi mea ʻoi aku ka nui
firmware: Hoʻopaʻa mau ʻia nā lako polokalamu ma kahi hāmeʻa (e like me ka BIOS)
overclocking: Ke holo nei i kahi CPU ma ka wikiwiki kiʻekiʻe ma mua o kāna mau kikoʻī i manaʻo ʻia
code ho\u02bboponopono hewa: ʻenehana e ʻike a hoʻoponopono i nā hewa ma RAM
ma waho o ka ho\u02bbok\u014d \u02bbana: ʻenehana kahi e hoʻokō ai ka CPU i nā ʻōlelo aʻo ma kahi ʻoi aku ka maikaʻi
helu helu quantum: Hoʻohana i nā loina o ka quantum mechanics no ka helu ʻana
ho\u02bbopili helu neuromorphic: Hoʻolālā ʻia ka lolouila hoʻonaʻauao no nā hana AI
